==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Detractor
<hw>De*tract"or</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.: cf. F.
<ets>d⟦eacute⟧tracteur</ets>.]</ety> <def>One who detracts; a derogator;
a defamer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His <qex>detractors</qex> were noisy and scurrilous.</q>
<rj><qau>Macaulay.</qau></rj></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Slanderer; calumniator; defamer;
vilifier.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Detractory</ent>⟦br⟧
